            <title>[FELIX-601] Reactivation of a component after a configuration update should be completely asynchronous</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-601</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the component is taken down immediately upon receiving new configuration. This may create issues when components are currently being activated. Therefore the cycling of the component after receiving configuration is to be scheduled for asynchronous execution.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
